               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of a work by Khvājah Aḥrār</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003807 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85014156 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh91002492" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1138-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian </textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Untitled spiritual biography of the saint and founder of the <orgName>Naqshbandī Ṣūfī</orgName> order, <persName key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658624.0x000001 viaf_6835087" role="subject">Bahāʾ al-Dīn Muḥammad Bukhārī the Naqshband</persName> (d. 791/1388), compiled by <persName key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658478.0x000001 viaf_485149294387580522619" role="aut">Khvājah ʿUbayd Allāh Aḥrār</persName> (d. circa 895/1490). 
                        </p>
                        <p>Not dated at end.  </p>
                        <p>Large proportions datable to mid to late sixteenth century, with replacement leaves from the seventeenth century. 
</p>
                        <p>Neat calligraphic nastaʿlīq. 
</p>
                        <p>Replacement folios 2, 154-169. 
</p>
                        <p>Persian and stamped foliation. 
</p>
                        <p>Original covers lost; front board of later delaminating leather binding only. </p>
                        <p>Folios partially bound; heavy water stains, wormholes, later repairs.
</p>
                        <p>Condition fragile. 
</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164658478.0x000001 viaf_485149294387580522619">Khvājah Aḥrār</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="viaf_485149294387580522619">خواجه احرار</persName>
                     </author>
                  </msItem>
